<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, March 14 (Xinhua) -- A total of 5.76 million US dollars
was fetched during the 33rd "Myanmar gems emporium" from the sale
of gems, jade and pearl lots through competitive bidding and at
fixed prices, state-run television reported today.
