title of his favourite event with a clearance of 2.31 meters,
which earned him the male athlete of the year award and 10,000
dollars (7,600 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Commonwealth champion Cathy Freeman won the women's 400 meters
event in 50.21 seconds and clinched the female athlete of the
year award.
</P>
<P>
Dean Capobianco won the 100 meters in 10.40 seconds. 
