In the last minute of the Espoli's 3-2 away loss to another
Ecuadorean team Barcelona, the cart which moved into the pitch to
carry off an injured player knocked over Valencia and he responded
by beating the driver.
</P>
<P>
The referee showed Valencia the red card and ordered him out of
the game in the first round of the South American tournament.
</P>
<P>
After a scoreless first half, Luis Gomez, Luis Alfaro Moreno
and Raul Noriega scored each for Barcelona, while Espoli's goals
came from Teodoro Jauch and Jose Goleas. 
