<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, March 14 (Xinhua)-- Sri Lanka is negotiating with the
Asian Development Bank (ADB) to repair the oil tanks which were
damaged when Tamil rebels attacked Colombo's oil installation last
year, according to local press reports today.
</P>
<P>
