the restoration of the tanks. This sum is likely to be enhanced
when the feasibility studies and estimates are submitted, the
reports said.
</P>
<P>
Tamil rebel attack on the oil tanks in the northern suburbs of
Colombo last October caused economic losses amounting to 60
million US dollars.  
