<HEADLINE> Edberg, Enqvist Out of Champions Cup Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 13 (Xinhua) -- A Swedish duo of Stefan Edberg
and Thomas Enqvist were all defeated in the second rounders of the
2.2 million U.S. dollars Champions Cup men's tennis in Indian
Wells, California on Wednesday.
</P>
